as%20trained%20using%20material%20unlawfully%20obtained%20from%20US%20AI%20models.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawmakers%20%E2%80%94%20Reps.%20John%20Moolenaar%2C%20a%20Republican%20from%20Michigan%2C%20and%20Raja%20Krishnamoorthi%2C%20a%20Democrat%20from%20Illinois%20%E2%80%94%20said%20it%20appeared%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-deepseek-r1-china-ai-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeepSeek%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20released%20a%20powerful%20AI%20model%20that%20made%20headlines%20in%20January%2C%20had%20used%2060%2C000%20chips%20from%20Nvidia%20despite%20US%20sanctions%20limiting%20the%20ability%20of%20the%20company%20to%20sell%20some%20of%20its%20hardware%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20is%20already%20having%20a%20tough%20week.%20Its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-price-investors-bad-year-deepseek-scare-tariffs-china-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estock%20fell%3C%2Fa%3E%20nearly%207%25%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20the%20company%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20been%20informed%20that%20the%20Trump%20administration%20would%20require%20a%20new%20license%20for%20all%20accelerated%20chips%20shipping%20to%20China.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20expected%20a%20%245.5%20billion%20decrease%20in%20earnings%20due%20to%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%20and%20a%20representative%20for%20Moolenaar%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20about%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeepSeek%20isn't%20just%20another%20AI%20app%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20weapon%20in%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party's%20arsenal%2C%20designed%20to%20spy%20on%20Americans%2C%20steal%20our%20technology%2C%20and%20subvert%20US%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Moolenaar%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20which%20called%20DeepSeek%20a%20%26quot%3Bserious%20national%20security%20threat%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawmakers%20said%20Nvidia%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E%20directed%20the%20design%20of%20chips%20to%20get%20around%20US%20export%20controls.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20Huang%20requesting%20lists%20of%20customers%20located%20in%20China%20and%20Southeast%20Asia%20and%20any%20communications%20between%20Nvidia%20and%20DeepSeek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20US%20government%20instructs%20American%20business%20on%20what%20they%20can%20sell%20and%20where%20%E2%80%94%20we%20follow%20the%20government's%20directions%20to%20the%20letter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20said%20it%20sells%20its%20products%20to%20companies%20worldwide%2C%20adding%20that%20its%20reported%20Singapore%20revenue%20indicates%20the%20billing%20addresses%20of%20its%20clients%2C%20many%20of%20which%20the%20company%20said%20are%20subsidiaries%20of%20US%20companies.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20associated%20products%20are%20shipped%20to%20other%20locations%2C%20including%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Taiwan%2C%20not%20to%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawmakers'%20report%20also%20found%20it%20was%20likely%20DeepSeek%20had%20deployed%20methods%20to%20copy%20leading%20AI%20models%20from%20US%20companies%2C%20violating%20those%20companies'%20terms%20of%20service.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20told%20lawmakers%20%26quot%3BDeepSeek%20employees%20circumvented%20guardrails%20in%20OpenAI's%20models%26quot%3B%20to%20accelerate%20the%20development%20of%20its%20own%20models%20at%20a%20lower%20cost%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-accuses-deepseek-using-ai-outputs-inappropriately-train-models-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20January%20it%20was%20investigating%20if%20DeepSeek%20used%20the%20outputs%20of%20its%20AI%20models%20to%20%26quot%3Binappropriately%26quot%3B%20train%20its%20own%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20found%20that%2085%25%20of%20responses%20from%20DeepSeek%20models%20purposefully%20suppress%20content%20related%20to%20democracy%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20and%20human%20rights%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recommendations%20in%20the%20report%20include%20increasing%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20US%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-deepseek-chip-restrictions-exports-imports-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexport%20control%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20further%20restricting%20China's%20ability%20to%20develop%20and%20deploy%20advanced%20AI%20models%20by%20expanding%20export%20controls%20on%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20encourage%20Congress%20to%20consider%20requiring%20that%20chips%20companies%20track%20the%20eventual%20user%20of%20their%20products%2C%20not%20just%20the%20purchaser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawmakers-deepseek-spying-china-nvidia-probed-chips-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744845199000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68002d973fe8d392836349f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawmakers-deepseek-spying-china-nvidia-probed-chips-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20lawmakers%20accused%20DeepSeek%20of%20spying%20for%20China%20and%20said%20they%20are%20looking%20into%20how%20Nvidia%20chips%20may%20have%20been%20obtained%20by%20the%20Chinese%20AI%20company.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40businessinsider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis%2CEmma%20Cosgrove)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A48%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawmakers-deepseek