%20the%20years%2C%20I've%20never%20been%20able%20to%20maintain%20a%20healthy%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20friendly%20bet%20with%20my%20wife%20changed%20everything%20though%2C%20and%20now%20I'm%20down%2021%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fdc0e8c4-1d80-4ecf-b2ab-406c0226183f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20partner%20with%20the%20same%20struggles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20met%20eight%20years%20ago%2C%20we%20were%20going%20through%20similar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-plateau-get-eating-fitness-back-on-track-advice-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweight%20struggles%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20at%20the%20gym%20and%20complained%20that%20she%20saw%20little%20to%20no%20results.%20With%20her%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20could%20always%20be%20myself%2C%20even%20show%20my%20body%20insecurities%20without%20fear%20of%20judgment.%20She%20understood%20my%20constant%20weight%20struggles%2C%20as%20I%20did%20hers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20we%20followed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-ways-keto-ruined-my-relationship-with-food-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKeto%20diet%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20try%20to%20eat%20more%20healthfully.%20For%20the%206%20months%20we%20committed%20to%20it%2C%20we%20didn't%20enjoy%20the%20food%20combinations%20that%20the%20diet%20offered%20and%20we%20ended%20up%20giving%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20trying%20to%20maintain%20a%20work-life%20balance%20and%20caring%20for%20our%20three%20kids%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20we%20had%20minimal%20time%20left%20for%20self-development.%20It%20got%20to%20a%20point%20where%20life%20was%20so%20busy%20that%20getting%20even%20an%20hour%20or%20two%20to%20spend%20at%20the%20gym%20felt%20luxurious.%20We%20knew%20the%20only%20way%20weight%20loss%20would%20work%20is%20if%20we%20incorporated%20it%20into%20our%209%20to%205%20routines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229ad5eecd-3452-45cf-b16c-49f5c1eae197%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20%245%2C000%20bet%20changed%20everything%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20noticed%20my%20wife%20frequently%20watching%20what%20has%20become%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BSkinnyTok%26quot%3B%20videos%20on%20TikTok.%20According%20to%20her%2C%20this%20content%20is%20how%20some%20creators%20give%20tips%20on%20losing%20weight%20and%20maintaining%20a%20healthy%20lifestyle.%20They%20also%20share%20recipes%20that%20are%20allegedly%20%26quot%3Bnutritious%20yet%20delicious.%26quot%3B%20Another%20creator%20particularly%20emphasized%20the%20power%20of%20walking%2010%2C000%20steps%20a%20day.%20I%20was%20curious.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMy%20wife%2C%20being%20the%20most%20competitive%20person%20I%20know%2C%20suggested%20that%20we%20take%20three%20months%2C%20cook%20some%20of%20the%20recipes%20she%20had%20been%20saving%2C%20walk%2010%2C000%20steps%20every%20day%2C%20and%20add%20in%20some%20cardio%20workouts.%20As%20an%20extra%20incentive%2C%20the%20person%20who%20lost%20the%20most%20weight%20would%20receive%20%245%2C000%20from%20our%20joint%20account%20to%20use%20it%20however%20they%20pleased.%20I%20was%20in!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220eeeec0e-fa46-471a-8eec-bc863b817e02%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20shared%20challenge%20was%20fun%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20into%20this%2C%20I%20knew%20two%20things%3A%20my%20wife%20would%20do%20everything%20she%20could%20to%20beat%20me%20and%20I%20would%20enjoy%20kicking%20her%20booty%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way.%20The%20significant%20amount%20of%20money%20on%20the%20line%20provided%20a%20lot%20of%20incentive%2C%20and%20thoughts%20of%20how%20my%20body%20would%20change%20for%20the%20better%20was%20what%20I%20needed%20for%20any%20extra%20push.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20prep%2C%20we%20wrote%20down%20ten%20healthy%20recipes%20we%20wanted%20to%20try%20and%20synced%20our%20devices%20to%20track%20each%20other's%20health%20activities.%20We%20started%20the%20challenge%20at%20the%20beg