three%20decades.%20It%20faced%20some%20competition%20from%20Volvo%20and%20others%2C%20but%20they%20never%20quite%20hit%20the%20mainstream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20of%20its%20successes%2C%20the%20Outback%20could%20not%20escape%20the%20struggles%20faced%20by%20the%20Legacy%20sedan%20in%20the%20marketplace.%20Sales%20dwindled%20to%20just%2019%2C600%20units%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubaru%20announced%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20that%20production%20of%20the%20Legacy%20will%20cease%20at%20the%20end%20of%202025%2C%20leaving%20the%20automaker%20without%20a%20sedan%20to%20serve%20as%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20Outback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223833%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20left%20side%20of%20a%20blue%202022%20Subaru%20Outback%20Wilderness%20Wagon%20parked.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68000c5bc6ad288d147e5984%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222555%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%202022%20Subaru%20Outback%20Wilderness.%3Cp%3ESubaru%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22be820716-0727-463d-8090-d4cc1ded58b2%5C%22%3EThere's%20actually%20a%20lot%20to%20like%20about%20the%20new%20Outback%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Outback%20might%20look%20drastically%20different%20from%20its%20predecessor%2C%20but%20many%20core%20elements%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Outback's%20engine%20options%20remain%20the%202.5-liter%20naturally%20aspirated%20and%20optional%202.4-liter%20turbocharged%20boxer%20four-cylinder%20motors.%20The%20revised%202.5-liter%20produces%20180%20horsepower%20and%20178%20lb-ft%20of%20torque%2C%20losing%20two%20ponies%20but%20gaining%20two%20lb-ft%20of%20torque%20compared%20to%20the%20outgoing%20model.%20The%20optional%20260-horsepower%20turbo%20motor%20shared%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubaru-ascent-suv-review-best-tech-features-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree-row%20Ascent%20SUV%3C%2Fa%3E%