with%20%2412%2C500%2C%20which%20they%20plan%20to%20use%20to%20build%20200%20of%20their%20refrigerators%20and%20send%20them%20to%20120%20hospitals%20for%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20hope%20their%20refrigerator%20can%20help%20transport%20vaccines%2C%20other%20medicines%20and%20supplies%2C%20and%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpast-noncompliance-barred-pig-transplant-patient-from-human-heart-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransplant%20organs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20able%20to%20keep%20the%20vaccines%20inside%20the%20Thermavault%20for%20almost%2010%20to%2012%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Pritesh%20Vyas%2C%20an%20orthopedic%20surgeon%20who%20tested%20the%20device%20at%20V%20One%20hospital%20in%20Indore%2C%20says%20in%20a%20video%20on%20the%20Thermavault%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthermavault.us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20some%20improvements%20like%20a%20built-in%20temperature%20monitor%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20will%20be%20definitely%20helpful%2C%20definitely%20useful%20in%20the%20remote%20places%2C%20the%20villages.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d0fefb72-ce23-4d69-a1be-84d153aa48fb%5C%22%3EFinding%20the%20right%20cooling%20salt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20salts%20can%20have%20a%20cooling%20effect%20when%20they're%20dissolved%20in%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20when%20those%20salts%20dissolve%2C%20the%20charged%20atoms%2C%20or%20ions%2C%20that%20make%20them%20up%20break%20apart.%20That%20separation%20requires%20energy%2C%20which%20the%20ions%20pull%20from%20the%20environment%2C%20thus%20cooling%20the%20water%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChaudhary%2C%20Ladhania%2C%20and%20Jain%20searched%20the%20internet%2C%20first%20compiling%20a%20list%20of%20about%20150%20salts%20that%20might%20work%2C%20then%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Enarrowing%20it%20down%20to%20about%2020%20that%20seemed%20most%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20then%20borrowed%20a%20lab%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institutes%20of%20Technology%20to%20test%20those%2020%2C%20or%20so.%20To%20their%20disappointment%2C%20none%20of%20the%20salts%20cooled%20the%20water%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20back%20to%20square%20one.%20Turns%20out%2C%20they%20didn't%20need%20the%20internet%20after%20all%20%E2%80%94%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-school-teacher-students-less-interested-college-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschool%20teacher%3C%2Fa%3E%20recommended%20trying%20two%20different%20salts%3A%20barium%20hydroxide%20octahydrate%20and%20ammonium%20chloride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20did%20scour%20through%20the%20entire%20internet%20to%20find%20the%20best%20salt%20possible%2C%20we%20kind%20of%20just%20ended%20up%20back%20to%20our%20ninth-grade%20science%20textbook%2C%26quot%3B%20Chaudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trio%20says%20they%20found%20that%20ammonium%20chloride%20maintained%20temperatures%20of%20around%202%20to%206%20degrees%20Celsius%20(about%2035%20to%2043%20degrees%20Fahrenheit)%2C%20which%20is%20ideal%20for%20many%20vaccines.%20Adding%20barium%20hydroxide%20octahydrate%20to%20the%20mix%20produced%20sub-zero%20Celsius%20temperatures%2C%20which%20is%20ideal%20for%20some%20other%20vaccines%20and%20sometimes%20for%20transplant%20organs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20they%20had%20two%20different%20refrigeration%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20three%20months%20later%2C%20they'd%20built%20a%20prototype%20and%20were%20testing%20it%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-wealthy-investors-got-rich-looting-needy-hospitals-healthcare-system-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocal%20hospitals%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2266aacf62-9937-4ac3-99e3-853005b8f925%5C%22%3EMeet%20the%20Thermavault%20salt%20refrigerator%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22thermavault%20refrigeration%20unit%20mockup%20shows%20a%20blue%20box%20with%20lid%20floating%20above%20it%20to%20show%20copper%20lining%20inside%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ffe622a466d2b74ab3550b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20mock-up%20of%20a%20Thermavault%20prototype.%3Cp%3EDhruv%20Chaudhary%2FMithran%20Ladhania%2FMridul%20Jain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fridge%20itself%20is%20an%20insulated%20plastic%20container%20with%20a%20copper%20wall%20lining%20the%20inside%2C%20where%20the%20vaccines%20or%20organs%20would%20sit.%20The%20cooling%20solution%2C%20made%20by%20dissolving%20the%20salts%20in%20water%2C%20is%20poured%20into%20a%20space%20between%20the%20plastic%20outer%20wall%20and%20the%20copper%20inner%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECold%20boxes%20and%20coolant%20packs%20are%20already%20in%20widespread%20use%20for%20bringing%20vaccines%20to%20rural%20areas%20without%20electricity.%20Those%20carriers%20typically%20rely%20on%20simple%20ice%20packs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20advantage%20of%20the%20ammonium%20chloride%20solution%2C%20the%20trio%20of%20teens%20says%2C%20is%20it's%20reusable%20in%20the%20field%20without%20electricity.%20You%20don't%20need%20a%20freezer%20to%20pull%20ice%20from.%20Rather%2C%20you%20can%20remove%20the%20salt%20water%20from%20the%20box%2C%20boil%20away%20the%20water%2C%20and%20collect%20the%20salt%20in%20its%20solid%20form%2C%20ready%20to%20dissolve%20in%20new%20water%20and%20produce%20its%20cooling%20effect%20all%20over%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJain%20said%20they're%20planning%20to%20use%20the%20prize%20money%20to%20pursue%20a%20Performance%2C%20Quality%20and%20Safety%20(PQS)%20certification%20through%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20so%20they%20can%20pitch%20it%20to%20Gavi%20%E2%80%94%20an%20international%20alliance%20that%20distributes%20vaccines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Earth%20Prize%20program%20also%20has%20a%20volunteer%20who%20can%20help%20them%20pursue%20a%20patent%2C%20according%20to%20a%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Earth%20Prize%20casts%20across%20the%20planet%20for%20teens%20who%20are%20working%20on%20environmental%20projects%20and%20awards%20one%20winner%20from%20each%20world%20region.%20Chaudhary%2C%20Ladhania%2C%20and%20Jain%20won%20the%20prize%20for%20Asia.%20A%20global%20winner%20will%20be%20chosen%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theearthprize.org%2Fvote%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epublic%20vote%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20closes%20on%20April%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteens-win-earth-prize-built-salt-powered-refrigerator-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744835035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fe6e16a466d2b74ab33004%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteens-win-earth-prize-built-salt-powered-refrigerator-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Thermavault%20refrigeration%20unit%20can%20keep%20vaccines%20cool%20with%20a%20reusable%20salt%20solution.%20The%20teens%20who%20built%20it%20plan%20to%20test%20it%20at%20120%20hospitals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mmcfalljohnsen%40businessinsider.com%20(Morgan%20McFall-Johnsen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A275%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteens-win-earth-prize-built-salt-powered-refrigerator-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI's%20latest%20move%20makes%20it%20harder%20for%20rivals%20like%20DeepSeek%20to%20copy%20its%20homework%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227488%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%2C%20wearing%20a%20suit%2C%20holding%20a%20laptop%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ff94f9c6