.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsustainable-architecture-1744381698.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsustainable-architecture-1744381698-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsustainable-architecture-1744381698-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsustainable-architecture-1744381698-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsustainable-architecture-1744381698-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-419769%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMoss%20walls%20require%20little%20maintenance%20and%20upkeep%20and%20act%20as%20great%20air%20purifiers%20to%20filter%20out%20volatile%20organic%20compounds.%20Picture%20source%3A%20GPM%20Architects%20and%20Planners%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20perk%20is%20that%20these%20%E2%80%98walls%E2%80%99%20double%20up%20as%20air%20purifiers%2C%20removing%20harmful%20VOCs%20(volatile%20organic%20compounds)%20from%20the%20ambient%20air%20while%20releasing%20fresh%2C%20pure%20oxygen.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20also%20help%20stabilise%20indoor%20humidity%20levels%2C%20maintaining%20a%20balanced%20microclimate.%20This%20creates%20a%20healthier%20environment%2C%20especially%20in%20office%20spaces%20with%20systems%20that%20can%20dry%20out%20the%20air%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mitu%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Owing%20to%20their%20sound%20absorption%20benefits%2C%20Mitu%20says%20moss%20walls%20should%20be%20installed%20strategically%20instead%20of%20just%20about%20anywhere.%20To%20maximise%20the%20sound%20absorption%20effect%2C%20she%20says%20architects%20could%20use%20a%20material%20behind%20the%20moss%20or%20opt%20for%20thicker%20layers%20of%20moss.%20%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20avoid%20excessive%20direct%20sunlight%2C%20as%20it%20can%20fade%20or%20dry%20out%20moss.%20Use%20artificial%20lighting%20strategically%20to%20prevent%20these%20effects%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mitu%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F325164533_Glued_laminated_timber_and_steel_beams_A_comparative_study_of_structural_design_economic_and_environmental_consequences%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlued%20laminated%20timber%20and%20steel%20beams%3A%20A%20comparative%20study%20of%20structural%20design%2C%20economic%20and%20environmental%20consequences%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Published%20in%20the%20Journal%20of%20Engineering%20Design%20and%20Technology%20in%20May%202018.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS2214509522000985%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20comparative%20study%20between%20glulam%20and%20concrete%20columns%20in%20view%20of%20design%2C%20economy%20and%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Published%20in%20Case%20Studies%20in%20Construction%20Materials%20in%20June%202022.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F241886678_Self-healing_of_lime_based_mortars_Microscopy_observations_on_case_studies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESelf-healing%20of%20lime%20based%20mortars%3A%20Microscopy%20observations%20on%20case%20studies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Published%20in%20January%202011.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-hea